{
  "key": 38532,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_PatrolStarkMountain",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Yo, if it isn’t {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
        "Out training right away, are you?\r",
        "So, uh, since you’re training anyway,\n",
        "can you do me a favor?\r",
        "I’d like you to patrol Stark Mountain\n",
        "for me."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_GoonsCausingTrouble",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Up past here, there’s this\n",
        "volcano. It’s Stark Mountain.\r",
        "Deep inside it is this special rock called\n",
        "the Magma Stone.\r",
        "I can’t explain it well, but it’s really\n",
        "important. It keeps a Pokémon asleep.\r",
        "But lately, I’ve been hearing rumors\n",
        "about vandals in Stark Mountain.\r",
        "They say goons in space suits are\n",
        "causing trouble there.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_WhatMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Huh?\n",
        "What, me?\r",
        "I was on my way to the Pokémon Center\n",
        "because my Pokémon’s low on HP.\r",
        "So, if you could get up to Stark\n",
        "Mountain now, that’d be great. Thanks!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_IllKeepAsking",
      "en_US": [
        "I’ll keep asking the same thing over and\n",
        "over until you say “Yes!”\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_YoureInCharge",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: OK! You’re in charge!\n",
        "Patrol Stark Mountain for me!\r",
        "Don’t worry about me.\n",
        "Not even a little bit, OK?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_IfItIsntPlayer",
      "en_US": [
        "Wake: Oh, if it isn’t {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
        "It’s been a while!\r",
        "You’ve grown so tough that you’re\n",
        "training out here now...\r",
        "Everyone keeps getting tougher and\n",
        "tougher...\r",
        "And, in doing that, they develop\n",
        "closer bonds with their Pokémon...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_ThatsMyMaster",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}: That’s my master!\n",
        "Those are words of wisdom!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_StillTroubleUnderstanding",
      "en_US": [
        "Wake: What? Are you still having trouble\n",
        "understanding?\r",
        "I don’t for a second ever recall\n",
        "accepting you as an apprentice!\r",
        "I mean, if it’s wrestling moves, I can\n",
        "show you all you like, but...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_DontBeThatWay",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}: Awww, master, don’t be\n",
        "that way!\r",
        "You’ve got to get me into that club\n",
        "in the Survival Area!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_BetterBeFullyPrepared",
      "en_US": [
        "Wake: ...How’d I get involved in this...?\r",
        "So, anyway, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}.\n",
        "You’re going to Stark Mountain?\r",
        "Even the wild Pokémon there are very,\n",
        "very tough...\r",
        "If your Pokémon aren’t well trained,\n",
        "they’ll have a miserable time...\r",
        "Then again, that kind of challenge\n",
        "is an exciting prospect...\r",
        "But no matter what, you’d better\n",
        "be fully prepared!\r",
        "I’ve got to get ready for another\n",
        "tournament. Farewell!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_OffToBattleFrontier",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}: You know, I think I got\n",
        "a little tougher again.\r",
        "That’s why I’m off to the Battle\n",
        "Frontier so I can make some challenges!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_WaitForMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Master!\n",
        "Wait for me!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_SignRt227StarkMountain",
      "en_US": [
        "Rt. 227\n",
        "Stark Mountain"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_Thorton_Prebattle",
      "en_US": [
        "Thorton: ...Hm. A subject appears.\n",
        "A Trainer bound for Stark Mountain.\r",
        "I am Thorton. I analyze data.\n",
        "Win ratios, movesets, patterns.\r",
        "Your records, however, are\n",
        "incomplete. I will collect them\f",
        "myself. Brace yourself.\f",
        "Consider this research."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_ThortonDefeated",
      "en_US": [
        "Thorton: Hmm...\n",
        "I got handed the loss here.\r",
        "It’s not making me happy at all, losing.\n",
        "Even though I’m not happy, I did glean\f",
        "some useful data, I suppose.\r",
        "That makes me glad I battled you.\r",
        "Please, take this as a reward."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_ThortonThatsVoltSwitchGoodbye",
      "en_US": [
        "Thorton: The data says it suits a\n",
        "Trainer of your type.\r",
        "TM75, Volt Switch. Strike, then\n",
        "withdraw. Highly efficient.\r",
        "I return to the Factory to revise\n",
        "my models. Farewell."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Route227_Text_ThortonLessThanTwoMons",
      "en_US": [
        "Thorton: Insufficient sample size.\r",
        "A proper analysis requires two\n",
        "Pokémon able to battle.\r",
        "Return once your team is ready.\n",
        "I will continue my observations."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
